you to cross over into the realm eternal.

the remaining ghosts will depart the area.

Oh, wow! Look at all these books!
Ehh. The last library I was in I was almost eaten by a \C[6]Bookwyrm\C[0].
O\..\..\..K\..\..\.. But look, these tomes are full of forgotten
knowledge. Histories and stories of the past.
For example. Here's a story about a demon with a magic absorbing
sword who was banished to an island for his crimes.
Gee, I wonder if he's still there?
Huh? What? Oh, I must have fallen asleep.
Let's get moving. I'm sure whatever creature this dusty old book
is on about is long gone by now.
